# Release v1.0 risk acceptances for dependency-only Trivy findings.
# The application does not enable Cloud Foundry actuator endpoints; health/metrics
# remain the only Compose-exposed actuator surfaces and the backend is bound to loopback.
CVE-2026-22733

# Spring Security 5.7.x is pinned to the latest public 5.7 patch for the Boot 2.7
# line. The Trivy DB lists only future 6.5.9/7.0.4 fixes, which are not available
# on Maven Central for this release baseline.
CVE-2026-22732

# This codebase does not expose HttpInvokerServiceExporter or Java deserialization
# remoting endpoints.
CVE-2016-1000027

# The backend does not use functional RouterFunctions with FileSystemResource.
# Static frontend assets are served by nginx, not Spring MVC.
CVE-2024-38816
CVE-2024-38819
